template.exportRequestEmailTemplate:
Subject: Request for data portability under {regulationCitation}

To {currentProvider},

Under {regulationCitation}, I request a copy of all personal data you hold about me, in a structured, commonly used, machine-readable format. This request covers: (1) account information, (2) usage history and transaction records, (3) content I have created or uploaded, (4) derived data and profiles.

Please provide the export within {statutoryDeadline} as required by law.

Account: {accountIdentifier}
Date of request: {today}

Sincerely,
{userName}
